{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d20b95d9-1a20-4319-9ff7-9517374e189c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d20b95d9-1a20-4319-9ff7-9517374e189c@1.pkg/1772597689763/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597689998", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d20b95d9-1a20-4319-9ff7-9517374e189c@1.pkg/1772597689763/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597689998"}, "identifier": "d20b95d9-1a20-4319-9ff7-9517374e189c", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查如何构建美好集体。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①：马卡连柯的这句话强调集体纪律的重要性，只有集体的纪律和规则得到保障，集体才能实现合力，保障共同利益，①符合题意。故①正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>②：集体规则是确保集体统一行动的重要基础和前提，因此②说法正确且符合题意，故②正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>③：&ldquo;集体规则与个人意愿必然会相互冲突&rdquo;说法过于绝对，在集体生活中个人意愿和集体规则并不必然发生冲突。因此③错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>④：纪律和规则在集体中十分重要，需要每个人自觉遵守。因此④说法正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①②④正确，因此选B</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）&ldquo;苏联教育家马卡连柯说：&ldquo;纪律是集体的面貌，集体的声音，集体的动作，集体的表情，集体的信念。&rdquo;对此，下列理解正确的是（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①纪律是集体利益能够实现的重要保障</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②集体规则是奏响和谐乐章的必要基础</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③集体规则与个人意愿必然会相互冲突</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④自觉遵守规则是共建美好集体的要求</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）“苏联教育家马卡连柯说：“纪律是集体的面貌，集体的声音，集体的动作，集体的表情，集体的信念。”对此，下列理解正确的是（    ）①纪律是集体利益能够实现的重要保障②集体规则是奏响和谐乐章的必要基础③集体规则与个人意愿必然会相互冲突④自觉遵守规则是共建美好集体的要求", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d20b95d9-1a20-4319-9ff7-9517374e189c@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977935209", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①②</span><span>③</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①</span><span>②④</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①③</span><span>④ &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②</span><span>③④</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "